sources.title: Killer Sex Queens From Cyberspace 1998 Lorissa Mc Comas, Danni Ashe, Glori Anne Gilbert, Michelle Monroe, Staci Alcorn, Nicole Hodson + Lou Vockell
sources.description: Amusing low budget film starring Lorissa McComas, Danni Ashe and Glori-Anne Gilbert. Some government agency has created a computer program called VICTIM that does something that somehow involves stock footage from early in Lorissa's career. She does not have a speaking role despite star billing.
